x4freetext: PILE Oscillator Facilities Of Dimpel Reactor
.Pile Oscillator Technique With A 1 Minute Period
And A Transition Time Of About 1.2 Second.
.The Neutron Temperature Was Determined By Using
The Non-1/V-absorbers  Sm-149, Cd-113 And Gd-natural
.Moderation Of Fast Neutrons By The Sample
.Error On The Boron Calibrations Less Than 1 Per Cent
.Error From The Uncertainty In Resonance Integral Of
Full Set Of References Added And Reaction
Dates were corrected for 4 digits year.
+ Correction in according to Memo CP-E/089.
Uppercase corrected in free text - MM/SM
